  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And there is no room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And no, you can't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "Ultimately, we came to a farm in [INAUDIBLE] where the farmer said, I, I can't house you on my property.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "There's an old, broken down chicory factory just 500 yards from, from the farm.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "If you can lodge there, you can work my fields.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And in exchange, I will give you food at night, a boiled potato, a hard boiled egg, and something else, some milk, for nourishment.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And so that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "We stayed in this, this broken down thing which had, of course, no, no facilities whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "There was a large shovel at the back door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "We would go into the back yard and dig a hole for hygienic purposes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And we slept on burlap bags, which were, of course, full of lice, as well at night, you could feel the mice running all over, over us as we were trying to sleep.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And we stayed with the farmer approximately seven, seven weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "My job-- the men had to go out and dig in the fields and harvest potatoes and beets and things of that nature.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "My job-- and now I'm going on 12-- and the farmer's daughter, who was the same age, our job was to take out little stools and a pail at 5 o'clock in the morning and go out into the field and milk the cows.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "I was a fast learner.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "I learned how to milk a cow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "What I didn't learn fast enough was how to deal with great, big, brown stallions who used to come up behind the cow and scare the cow away and then drink the milk, [LAUGHS] along with any number of cats and kitties that were very anxious for the milk as well.",
      "word_count": 51
    }
  ],
